@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About ASCEND";
}

<div class="glass-card" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem; border-radius: 24px;">
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
        <h1 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: 2px;">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-angles-up" style="color: var(--color-primary); filter: drop-shadow(0 0 8px var(--glow-color)); margin-right: 8px;"></i>ASCEND
        </h1>
        <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 6px;">"One App. Many Worlds. Endless Growth."</p>
    </div>

    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; line-height: 1.7;">
        <div>
            <h3 style="font-family: var(--font-display); color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">The Core Philosophy</h3>
            <p>ASCEND is built on the principle of self-gamification. By treating real-life habits as daily quests and assigning them RPG parameters (XP, difficulty levels, streaks, and ranks), ASCEND transforms the monotony of daily routines into an engaging progression system. Level up your habits, level up your life.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
            <h3 style="font-family: var(--font-display); color: var(--color-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">The Multi-Dimensional Experience</h3>
            <p>Each theme in ASCEND represents a different "Dimension" or fantasy realm. Whether you are hunting in the neon shadows of the <strong>Shadow Hunter</strong> world, drifting through the peaceful blossoms of <strong>Sakura Ascension</strong>, gazing at the stars in the <strong>Celestial Realm</strong>, or protecting the ancient woods in the <strong>Forest Guardian</strong> forest, the application adapts its visual language, sound systems, and animations to keep your productivity journey immersive and fresh.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border-glass); padding-top: 2rem; margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); text-align: center;">
            <p>© 2026 ASCEND System. Created for academic and productivity excellence. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
